    <h1>EXAM INSTRUCTIONS</h1>
    <p>All the tasks in our Evaluation should be performed on <strong>“clone-client” Machine Only</strong>.</p>
    <hr>

    <h2>On clone-Server:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Create a directory <strong>RHCSA-2025</strong> on clone-server.</li>
        <li>CD into <strong>RHCSA-2025</strong> and run the following commands:</li>
        <pre>
cd RHCSA-2025
git clone https://github.com/saim-ali-hub/batch-2025-server.git
cd batch-2025-server
./server-config.sh
        </pre>
        <li>Open a browser and go to: <strong>&lt;server’s ip-address&gt;/.saim_repo</strong>. Open each file in a new window.</li>
        <li>Read question number 1 and switch to clone-client.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>On clone-Client:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Create a directory <strong>RHCSA-2025</strong> on clone-client.</li>
        <li>CD into <strong>RHCSA-2025</strong> and run the following commands:</li>
        <pre>
cd RHCSA-2025
git clone https://github.com/saim-ali-hub/batch-2025-client.git
cd batch-2025-client
./clone-client-mess-up            (For Client machine configuraton)
./RHCSA-evaluator-2025            (For validation of tasks)
        </pre>
    </ul>

    <p class="important">IMPORTANT NOTE: DON'T OPEN OR READ THE SCRIPTS. OTHERWISE THERE IS NO POINT TO TAKE THIS EVALUATION.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Password Instructions:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>When recovering root password, please set the new root password to <strong>redhat</strong>.</li>
        <li>Use the same password for all users you create or for login to any user account.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Network Instructions:</h2>
    <p>If you have a different network, you can use that network address, but host address should be <strong>xxx.xxx.x.130</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Yum Repository URLs</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>BaseOS: <a href="http://3.84.128.134/repos/rhel9/BaseOS/" target="_blank">http://3.84.128.134/repos/rhel9/BaseOS/</a></li>
        <li>AppStream: <a href="http://3.84.128.134/repos/rhel9/AppStream/" target="_blank">http://3.84.128.134/repos/rhel9/AppStream/</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Container Image Registry</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Registry: <strong>registry.redhat.io</strong></li>
        <li>Username: &lt;your redhat username&gt;</li>
        <li>Password: &lt;your redhat password&gt;</li>
    </ul>

    <p>At the end of the exam, <strong>reboot the system</strong>.</p>

